I am sure you have noticed something interesting about the lead of an honor by the declarer. Yes, you guessed right. Declarer led an honor and dummy had an honor directly below the one that was led. If West thinks as most declarers do, it would be apparent that when declarer leads an honor and dummy does not have the honor immediately below then declarer must have that honor. |
