Your only hope is that the Declarer will consider the possibility too remote that you have Queen-Jack and do not play one of them, and will simply, as a matter of safety first, go up with the Ace, hoping that the suit will ultimately break to his advantage. You see, to play the Jack here, flaunting it in the face of Dummy's powerful holding, will give away the whole situation. |
